We hope you “treasure every encounter” when you’re learning about our masters and their objets d’ art.
Ultimately, we don’t curate just beautiful pieces of art but also the incredible people who create them.

We’ll share their inspiration, design, and craftsmanship. Most of all,
we’ll convey their passion for their life’s work.

At Ichigoichie Galerie, we’re deeply honored to work with many masters
of their craft and have the distinct pleasure to introduce them to u.
However, we see these works of art less as precious objects than rich experiences―ones to cherish and share with others.

Ichigo-ichie” is a famous Japanese saying that means “treasure every
encounter.” This profound thought inspired our gallery.
